{"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuser:emails:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"setUser:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"userId","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"emails:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray","text":"NSArray"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"emails","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The custom user identifier.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"userId"},{"name":"emails","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Array of email address strings to associate with the user."}]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Convenience method that combines "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setUserId:"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setEmails:"},{"text":" into a single","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"server request. This is more efficient than calling both methods separately","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and ensures atomic association of user ID with emails.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this during login or registration flows when you have both user ID"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and email available simultaneously.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Example","level":2,"anchor":"Example","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Complete registration with user ID and emails:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class RegistrationManager {","","    func completeRegistration(_ registration: RegistrationData) {","        \/\/ Create user on backend","        APIClient.shared.createUser(registration) { result in","            guard case .success(let user) = result else { return }","","            \/\/ Set both user ID and emails in single operation","            var emails = [user.email]","            if let secondaryEmail = registration.secondaryEmail {","                emails.append(secondaryEmail)","            }","","            Pushwoosh.configure.setUser(user.id, emails: emails)","","            \/\/ Set initial user tags","            Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                \"registration_date\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","                \"registration_source\": registration.source.rawValue,","                \"account_type\": user.accountType.rawValue,","                \"has_completed_onboarding\": false","            ])","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["   when you need confirmation."]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets user identifier and emails together in a single operation."}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"title":"setUser:emails:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUser:emails:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setUser:emails:","kind":"identifier